    "body": "I've had some lenovo yoga users report issues with highlighting text and resizing textareas. The videos I've [been sent](https://github.com/Thomas101/wmail/issues/334#issuecomment-251073247) seem to be similar to the video @CharlieHess uploaded. Was not able to reproduce the issues on non-lenovo laptops though.\n\nI've attached the simplest example I could put together... [wmail-lenovo-test copy.zip](https://github.com/electron/electron/files/548229/wmail-lenovo-test.copy.zip) and also a [prebuilt version](https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B--sEKXlbUTRZ09FYVhYSDlwaTQ) ... a video of the bug that came through for me was [uploaded here](https://sendvid.com/5bq2ftax).\n\nI'd hate to hijack your issue so if it all works for you I'm happy to open elsewhere but on the face of it looks like it might be related :-/\n"
